snippet.title: Grappling Hook - Trailer
snippet.description:
Special Offer: Every 10th Order is FREE!
Take your chance and get your copy of Grappling Hook for FREE PLUS a 50 % OFF COUPON for a friend!
Read more about it here: http://ghook.speedrungames.com/

Free demo for Windows, Mac, & Linux available at: http://ghook.speedrungames.com/

Grappling Hook is a first-person action puzzle / platform game.

Core-Features:
1. Grappling Hook as a mighty tool to perform daring moves and tricks
2. Challenging gameplay and action puzzles
3. 22 dynamic, animated, and unique levels
4. 30 cool achievements and 4 challenges for every level

Available for Windows, Mac OS X, & Linux!

Website: http://ghook.speedrungames.com/
Music by Silence (Cellule).
